article_author: ['Foto', 'Pap Epa Interior Ministry Press Service Handout', 'Grzegorz Jakubowski', 'Kprp', 'Pap Epa John Thys', 'Pap Radek Pietruszka']
article_text:
"Najbliższe dni, tygodnie i miesiące będą ciężkie dla mieszkańców Ukrainy. Putin zgotował im wielki ból" - napisał na Twitterze prezydent USA Joe Biden.

The next few days, weeks, and months will be hard on the people of Ukraine. Putin has unleashed a great pain on them.



But the Ukrainian people have known 30 years of independence — and they have shown that they will not tolerate anyone who tries to take their country backwards.
